    <thetext>The following syntax for definition lists

   ; Definition list term
   : Definition list data item
   : Another data item

and

   - coffee := Hot _and_ black
   - tea := Also hot, but a little less black
   - milk := Nourishing beverage for baby cows.
   Cold drink that goes great with cookies. =:

is not currently supported by WikiText Textile rendered.

See http://redcloth.org/textile/page-layout/#definition-lists or http://txstyle.org/doc/10/definition-lists for syntax detail.</thetext>
