    <thetext>cheat sheet: https://git.eclipse.org/r/15076

initial implementation is complete

supported syntax examples follow:

native Textile syntax

bc. 
- term := definition
- term two := a multi-
line definition =:
- term three := definition 3

mediawiki-style syntax

bc. 
; term
: definition
; another term
: second definition
: third definition</thetext>
